,</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></mfenced></math></span>. The graph of the parametric function&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"g\"><math alttext=\"g\"><mi>g</mi></math></span>&nbsp;is given by&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"g open parentheses t close parentheses equals open parentheses x open parentheses t close parentheses comma y open parentheses t close parentheses close parentheses\"><math alttext=\"g open parentheses t close parentheses equals open parentheses x open parentheses t close parentheses comma y open parentheses t close parentheses close parentheses\"><mi>g</mi><mfenced><mi>t</mi></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mfenced><mrow><mi>x</mi><mfenced><mi>t</mi></mfenced><mo>,</mo><mi>y</mi><mfenced><mi>t</mi></mfenced></mrow></mfenced></math></span>, where&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"x open parentheses t close parentheses equals 5 plus 2 cos t\"><math alttext=\"x open parentheses t close parentheses equals 5 plus 2 cos t\"><mi>x</mi><mfenced><mi>t</mi></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>cos</mi><mi>t</mi></math></span>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"y open parentheses t close parentheses equals 5 plus 2 sin t\"><math alttext=\"y open parentheses t close parentheses equals 5 plus 2 sin t\"><mi>y</mi><mfenced><mi>t</mi></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>sin</mi><mi>t</mi></math></span>&nbsp;for&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"0 less or equal than t less or equal than 2 pi\"><math alttext=\"0 less or equal than t less or equal than 2 pi\"><mn>0</mn><mo>≤</mo><mi>t</mi><mo>≤</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi></math></span>.&nbsp;</p><p class=\"dap_body\">The graph of&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"g\"><math alttext=\"g\"><mi>g</mi></math></span>&nbsp;is a transformation of the graph of&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"f\"><math alttext=\"f\"><mi>f</mi></math></span>. Which of the following statements is true with the correct reasoning?</p> </div> </div> </div>\n",
